headline: Cboe Global Markets (CBOE): Revisiting Valuation After a Strong Multi‑Year Run and Recent Share Price Pullback
summary: Cboe Global Markets (CBOE) has been drifting slightly lower over the past week, even after a strong run this year. This makes now a good moment to revisit what the market is pricing in. See our latest analysis for Cboe Global Markets. With the share price now at $252.76, the recent 7 day share price pullback contrasts with its double digit 90 day share price return and powerful multi year total shareholder returns. This suggests momentum is cooling, while the longer term trend remains firmly...
